NEAR Protocol Airdrop

The NEAR Airdrop is a promotional campaign by the NEAR Protocol aimed at increasing the circulation and visibility of the $NEAR token. This is part of a broader effort to build a robust and active community around NEARs scalable blockchain solutions.
2,000 $NEAR is claimable for every reward voucher holder.
